===Etymology 1===
{{zh-forms|s=厌|alt=猒,懕}}

Sagart, Jacques et al. (2019) identify this word as cognate to {{cog|sit-tan-pro|*jem|t=to be satiated, tired}}. 

A proto-form that could unite these two forms could be {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*ʔjem}}.

