# to be [[fed up]] with; to grow [[bored]] of; to become [[tired]] of
#* {{quote-book|zh|title=The Beginner's First Book in the Chinese Language, (Canton Vernacular)|author=Thomas T. Devan|year=1847|publisher=The "China Mail" Office|location=Hongkong|page=91|pageurl=https://en.wikisource.org/w/index.php?title=File%3AThe_beginner%27s_first_book_in_the_Chinese_language.pdf&page=106}}
