#* {{quote-book|zh|title=雷雨|author={{w|Cao Yu}}|year=1939|edition=14th|origyear=1934|publisher=文化生活出版社|page=88|pageurl=https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?title=File%3ASSID-12661337_%E9%9B%B7%E9%9B%A8.pdf&page=108}}
#*: {{zh-q|但是 這兒{r} 我 住 厭 了。|But I've grown tired of living here.}}
# to [[detest]]; to [[dislike]]; to [[hate]]
#: {{zh-x|厭世|to be world-weary}}
